
make a release

# 1 full release

All otp/user applications are copied, with version, to this location:

    var/erlang/<app>/lib/..

ERTS execuatbles are copied here:

    var/erlang/<app>/erts-<vsn>/...

Executables and scripts are copied here:

    var/erlang/<app>/bin/...

Releases are located here, referenced from scripts if used. Entries
are symlinks pointing to var/erlang/<app>/lib

    var/erlang/<app>/rel/<rel-vsn>/<lib-symlink>

example:

    var/erlang/foo/rel/1.1/bar -> var/erlang/foo/lib/bar-4.5

Applications start and config are located here:

    ets/erlang/<app>/
